reviews.text: The dim sum in this place extremely satisfying. The staff were friendly and overall I had a great experience.
A very nice chinese resaurant in the centre of TST East. Some of their daily offers area really attractive where you must not miss.
Dim sum here is good. Spacious restaurant. Reasonable price.
We hired a private room for meeting with friends. Service was good and we had a great evening. Some mix ups with the food we had pre-ordered, which was a minor annoyance, but largely resolved
Good food and place at reasonable price. Lobsters are particularly great !
